The comedian is currently sporting a short hairdo and she explained that a problem with relaxer forced her to change her look.She was on air with DJ Fresh and the rest of the Fresh Breakfast team."The lady who did my hair put relaxer on my hair so I can put on my weave. Then when I took off the weave, I looked like a cat. You know, like that cat-weird fluffy situation? So I decided let's just shave it and restart," she said.The comedian explained that in an effort to look beautiful for the SAFTAs had a mohwak weave.A post shared by Tumi Morake (@tumi_morake) on Mar 18, 2017 at 10:29am PDT 